<mvc:View controllerName="journeyPlanner.JourneyPlanner.controller.Worklist" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:semantic="sap.m.semantic">
	<Page title="MMap your Ride">
		<content>
			<HBox>
				<VBox>
					<GenericTile class="sapUiLargeMarginBegin sapUiLargeMarginTop smartJourneyPlannerWorklistTiles" 
						busyIndicatorDelay="{worklistView>/tableBusyDelay}" 
						press="onRealTimeTilePress" 
						backgroundImage="images/RealTimeCrowd.jpg">
					</GenericTile>
					<HBox class="sapUiLargeMarginBegin" justifyContent="Center">
						<Text text="Ride Now" class="smartJourneyPlannerTileText"/>
					</HBox>
				</VBox>
				<VBox>
					<GenericTile class="sapUiMediumMarginBegin sapUiLargeMarginTop smartJourneyPlannerWorklistTiles" 
						busyIndicatorDelay="{worklistView>/tableBusyDelay}" 
						press="onHistoryTilePress" 
						backgroundImage="images/HistoricalCrowd.jpg">
					</GenericTile>
					<HBox class="sapUiMediumMarginBegin" justifyContent="Center">
						<Text text="Check my Station" class="smartJourneyPlannerTileText"/>
					</HBox>
				</VBox>
			</HBox>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>